Subject: Unable to save schedule job settings
Description: I created some job schedule on netwrix enterprise auditor and was unable to save the settings. The application returned an unspecified error, kindly assist.
Solution_Comment__c:
AD service account hasn't had permission to run the scheduled tasks because there was no role assigned in the NEA console to this account.
Once the "Administrator" role was assigned to this service account the scheduled tasks started to kick off.
